{"tid":2005831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署：建議相關人士盡快聯絡投訴調查組","createTime":"2020-05-07T11:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T13:45:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd12ddc82c37c5c5813c0a577baf6c73e7bac1b","tid":2005831,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"懲教署：被指暴力對待反修例人士的懲教助理按編更休假<br />\n07.05.2020 18:56<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志早前指控懲教人員暴力對待反修例人士，並指涉事的懲教助理目前經已休假，懲教署回覆查詢時指，相關人員只是按編更安排放假，假期後會返回壁屋懲教所工作。懲教署指，投訴調查組正調查事件，又建議相關人士盡快聯絡投訴調查組，以讓署方調查。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志早前指，有早前還押、目前獲保釋的人，2月在壁屋懲教所時唱反修例歌曲，數天後被一名職員掌摑，又被命令自摑，批評懲教人員酷刑對待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285885&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1285885%26csid%3D261_341&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=8a4045a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285885&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"cef579e1f84dc675e17a3d7e1af60f0662126100","tid":2005831,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"同警察投訴課有咩分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfbe93941ea331bea85cfa4f6c0ad672984685d","tid":2005831,"uid":200070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"聯絡完跟住俾你打鑊甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1554e8b283520d439679729bffdade7e8995907","tid":2005831,"uid":324041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"跟住就有專人上門，打完心口打背脊㗎啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab85be